Titolo: The Adventures of Maddog Williams in the Dungeons of Duridian

Anno: 1992

Descrizione: The Adventures of Maddog Williams in the Dungeons of Duridian is a 1992 video game developed by Game Crafter. The game is a cross between a text adventure and a role-playing game in which the player assumes the role of Maddog Williams, a shopkeeper and inventor from the seaside town of Marinor.
Maddog Williams was released on Amiga, Atari ST and DOS and a sequel was planned for release titled Escape from Cylindria. Currently the game is freely available for download from the developers' website.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
